Rebecca Ryan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rebecca_Ryan 0 Rebecca Ryan (born 27 April 1991) is an English actress. She attended St Monica's High School in Manchester. Ryan is best known for playing the role of Debbie Gallagher in the Channel 4 comedy drama series Shameless from 2004 to 2009 and as Vicki MacDonald in the BBC school-based drama series, Waterloo Road from 2009 to 2011. She has appeared in the UK tour of Beryl, written by her former Shameless co-star, Maxine Peake, who played Veronica Ball. Rebecca_Ryan ( born 27_April_1991 ) is an_English_actress .
